{"id": 2770, "genre": 1000, "title": "你在和朋友相处时，都是怎样避免索取式 social 的？", "description": "虽说互相麻烦也是一种增进感情的方式，但麻烦添多了也可能会消耗友情。（题图来自：iStock ©️ CSA-Printstock）", "record_count": 25291, "comment_count": 32, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190129162512d3buQ8srJRNpXWCt.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-31T17:42:13Z", "questions": [{"id": 5318, "title": "你在和朋友相处时，都是怎样避免索取式 social 的？", "content": "你在和朋友相处时会避免哪些索取式 social？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 325257, "content": "不为集福卡加一堆支付宝好友", "image": "img/option/option/201901291652273FHmPqBaneJwMUtI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325264, "content": "从来没在朋友圈求过赞 ", "image": "img/option/option/20190129171007ghu2S4vGyaIRVnd5.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325265, "content": "不请朋友帮忙代购大件物品", "image": "img/option/option/201901291707397gWITsLPNl9oeGKU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325266, "content": "不直接问朋友网上能搜索到答案的问题", "image": "img/option/option/20190129170752WRusMc1NJYh954i8.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325268, "content": "说过的事先找聊天记录，而不是每次都重新问", "image": "img/option/option/20190129170802nZa32HNUJPifgmFs.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325271, "content": "聊近况的时候不光说自己，也把对方的听进去", "image": "img/option/option/20190129170816uXso3bwamjYJnVQ6.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325274, "content": "约吃饭如果对方买单，把自己那份主动转账", "image": "img/option/option/201901291708373EPsdxlbHM0kczph.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325281, "content": "一起出去玩/打球时，轮流买吃的喝的", "image": "img/option/option/20190129170850JOPCfNdEhAxI0Qim.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325282, "content": "有事找人帮忙时才发现没加对方好友，就，放弃了", "image": "img/option/option/20190129170914sXCOYgkmTAMqnVLD.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 325283, "content": "临时要去朋友所在地出差，怕麻烦对方干脆就不说了", "image": "img/option/option/201901291709261FaQBbscqSxDruIR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}